						               													<description>Salt &amp;amp; Burn is a tabletop competitive action/adventure board game about hunting supernatural creatures. With 2-6 players, each person draws a randomly selected character card with health and damage stats, and a random vehicle card. There are 12 unique Angel, Human and Demon Hunter character cards, each with different stats for health and damage and different benefits based on species&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Throughout the game you can collect item cards that modify your health or damage, and collect trunk cards which are like spells that you can save and cast during your turn to help you or hinder other hunters. If you die during the course of a fight, you will have to go to Purgatory until you roll a 3 and return to the start of the game without any of your worldly possessions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players travel the game board to hunt down monsters. Monsters are drawn at random along with other Event cards for an element of surprise. The more monsters you kill, the more lives you save. If you kill a particularly dangerous monster, you'll save more lives in the process, and win the game faster. The first hunter to save 10 lives wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
